{"tid":1435745,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"拒收中銀鈔票","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:18:27.000Z","uid":178470,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3d39433546538acf6f529f52e3cb89f37e9d3298","tid":1435745,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"杯葛中銀就取消銀行戶口啦<br />\n但如果我冇中銀戶口<br />\n拒收中銀發行既鈔票<br />\n令中銀鈔票係市面唔流通<br />\n會唔會對中銀有影響？"},{"pid":"7bd1f00631e6b37d8015257425380ee82c5c62bf","tid":1435745,"uid":178470,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"出街食飯<br />\n找錢見到有中銀銀紙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該同我換過張</span></span>"},{"pid":"accc870e8b65c3dddbbcd8e598be3fb8fba2c2ca","tid":1435745,"uid":157516,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"全城不合作運動，等佢變廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7020b9f53171a1bada3863f45f678af931fc0e","tid":1435745,"uid":178470,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"去櫃員機撳錢出中銀鈔票<br />\n<br />\n行返入銀行櫃檯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">張銀紙好污糟，唔該幫我換咗佢</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a5b483e6f81e4ea390777a626656bee72aa265a0","tid":1435745,"uid":190383,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"拒收法定貨幣好似犯法"},{"pid":"a8387a1dff7e50655b5e774f257a3a83eaac2aab","tid":1435745,"uid":178470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5b483e6f81e4ea390777a626656bee72aa265a0","tid":1435745,"uid":190383,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"拒收法定貨幣好似犯法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"咁佢真係好污糟呀嘛<br />\n整污糟我銀包就唔好啦"},{"pid":"c2b982724c9bb3c5934700846f5559506f886853","tid":1435745,"uid":22822,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5b483